{"body": "Using `:rubygems` in the Gemfile means that it's actually accessing http://rubygems.org instead of https.  I'd like to propose that we revert this change as I think https is a better default.  Thoughts?\r\n\r\n\r\nFYI - Some time back I had submitted a pull request to bundler to change the default usage of `:rubygems` to be https but it was not merged due to SemVer.  More info here: https://github.com/carlhuda/bundler/pull/1585", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3669834", "created_at": "2012-01-26T14:44:46Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/4684#issuecomment-3669834", "updated_at": "2012-01-26T14:44:46Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 4684, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/spagalloco", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/6cb846fa3915943695482f6bf78084b7?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F79aadfd37377569522c12e25d973b68e.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/received_events", "gravatar_id": "6cb846fa3915943695482f6bf78084b7", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "spagalloco", "type": "User", "id": 28044, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/spagalloco/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52382295bd3543c15100eac0"}, "id": 3669834, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/4684"}
